{"TopicId":180044,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"Some way to read off orientation of the Internal View camera?","CreatedByName":"willwill2will","CreatedById":188654,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-24T17:52:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"willwill2will","CreatedById":188654,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-24T17:52:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am working on a project that requires the ability to check the direction the camera is facing when in internal view\u00A0mode. I have been searching the docs, and have looked at the source code of mods like KerbTrack, and have turned up nothing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs an inexperienced modder,\u00A0I was hoping that someone would be able to point me in the right direction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-11-24T18:15:36Z\u0022 title=\u002211/24/2018 06:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 24, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by willwill2will\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ger_space","CreatedById":167349,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T06:23:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCamera.gameobject.transform.forward\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere camera is the cam you are referring too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"willwill2will","CreatedById":188654,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T15:44:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167349\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ger_space\u003C/a\u003E. I will give this a go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-11-26T15:45:15Z\u0022 title=\u002211/26/2018 03:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 26, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by willwill2will\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}